steps.html_instructions: Head north on Capitol Ave SW toward Martin Luther King Jr Dr SW
Take the 1st left onto Martin Luther King Jr Dr SW

Turn right to merge onto I-20 W
Entering Alabama
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-459 S/Montgomery/Tuscaloosa and merge onto I-459 S

Take the exit on the left onto I-20 W/I-59 S toward Tuscaloosa
Entering Mississippi
Keep right at the fork to continue on I-20 W, follow signs for Jackson
Take exit 46 for Interstate 55 N toward North Jackson/Grenada
Keep right to continue on Access Rd/Fairgrounds St

Continue onto Fairground St/E Pearl St
Continue to follow E Pearl St
